From 27c137449bca2d034fe3227df26da6b05afd1504 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: SlayZone Dev <dev@slayzone.local>
Date: Sat, 18 Apr 2026 13:41:10 +0200
Subject: [8/9] slayzone: Phase 5.1 SlayzoneBrowserView scaffold + layout-shell
 feature
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Subclass of BrowserView, gated on slayzone::kSlayzoneLayoutShell
(default-on). Zero behavior change in this patch — Phase 5.2 populates the
region container. Factory branches on the feature, falling back to upstream
BrowserView when disabled for A/B + bisect.
---
